r-salat-jamaah","tag-day-of-resurrection","tag-glad-tidings-al-bushra","tag-good-deeds-hasanat","tag-hereafter-akhirah","tag-light-al-nur-noor","tag-manners-adab","tag-mosques-masjid","tag-prayer-al-salat","tag-reward-al-ajr"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-48f","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":19485,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/07\/14\/masajid-iman-visit-often\/","url_meta":{"origin":15887,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Mosques: Affirm faith of those who frequent the masjid","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 14, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Sa\u2019id reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cIf you see a man committed to the mosque, bear witness to his faith. Verily, Allah Almighty said: The mosques are only maintained by those who have faith in Allah and the Last Day, establish prayer\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":11580,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/01\/22\/dua-salat-ala-al-nabi-most\/","url_meta":{"origin":15887,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Salawat: Nearest to Prophet blessed him most","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 22, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe closest of people to me on the Day of Resurrection are those who sent the most blessings upon me.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 484 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Tirmidhi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\